article_title: Palestinian media: Several killed in Israeli strikes on Nuseirat refugee camp.
sentence: In  the  last  few  hours  we've  seen  reports  from  Palestinian  news  outlets  of  several  people  killed  from  Israeli  strikes  on  the  Nuseirat  refugee  camp  in  central  Gaza.

article_title: Palestinian media: Several killed in Israeli strikes on Nuseirat refugee camp.
sentence: News  agency  Wafa  said  17  people  were  killed,  while  news  outlet  Palestinian  Information  Center  put  the  figure  as  15  with  "a  large  number"  still  under  the  rubble.
